{"tid":1585001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一大班人係到放風割急救手足","createTime":"2019-09-21T11:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T12:06:00.000Z","uid":67292,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aee2429360dbdfe5a5dcb5c64f48c6560dba2fe8","tid":1585001,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"大家割急救員之前有無諗過點解黑警會捉到果幾個急救員？<br />\n<br />\n係因為急救員一般除左急救，亦都會幫手<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇水同殿後</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n今日下午我發夢係現場，果幾個急救手足比黑警捉，係因為黑警衝既時候殿後，先比d無耐性既popo捉黎洩憤。<br />\n<br />\n行得出黎做急救既，當然係為左手足安全，所以我地會盡一切能力同方法去保障手足唔好被捕或者受傷。有救急手足被捕就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">一大班人係到割席</span></span>，係五毛定冷氣私怨撚上身？"},{"pid":"02c9f4c175ab9a170bedf841155b27b7f82fbc24","tid":1585001,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:50:24.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c17c08e3db4e06a6209943d47c79de72bdd7d96","tid":1585001,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"見到d割席post就嬲"},{"pid":"02bbc4b7596d1f44c996c6f8ef0274e52bbd5b71","tid":1585001,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"成日係到屌急救員果d到底有無落過場？"},{"pid":"09a1f8729f6eb68847a2d7df17e1487aeb780a3f","tid":1585001,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:53:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89